        "richtext_wk6Wpg": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Revive and Nourish Your Hands with Our Hand Wash & Hand Creams</h2><p>Treat your hands to luxurious care with Mumu Bath's range of <strong>hand wash and hand creams</strong>. Each product is crafted to cleanse, hydrate, and protect your skin, leaving your hands soft and beautifully nourished. Whether you're looking for a simple hand wash or a complete hand care duo, our collection is designed to provide gentle, long-lasting moisture and protection.</p><h3>Hand Wash: Gentle Cleansing with a Luxe Feel</h3><p>Our hand wash is formulated to cleanse and refresh your hands without stripping away essential moisture. Packed with nourishing ingredients, it leaves your skin feeling clean, soft, and delicately scented.</p><h3>Revive & Restore Hand Care Duo: The Perfect Pair</h3><p>For the ultimate hand care experience, our <strong>Revive & Restore Hand Care Duo</strong> combines a hydrating hand wash with a deeply moisturizing hand lotion. This set is perfect for those who want to keep their hands feeling smooth, moisturized, and pampered throughout the day.</p><h3>Long-Lasting Hydration with Hand Lotion</h3><p>Infused with nourishing ingredients, our hand lotion is lightweight but provides deep hydration. Ideal for dry or tired hands, this lotion is fast-absorbing, leaving your skin feeling soft and refreshed without a greasy residue.</p>"
          }
